      • SpatialObjectTabController

        public SpatialObjectTabController(SpatialObjectsTab spatialObjectsTab)
        Constructor creates to separated views. One is for showing table with all spatial objects saved in the database and second is for showing and editing details about one specific spatial object. View with table is displayed.
        Parameters:
        spatialObjectsTab - instance of the spatial objects tab view
